  | Soft Link                          | Hard Link                                    |
| ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `ln -s source link`                | `ln source link`                             |
| Has a different inode              | Same inode as original file                  |
| Can link across filesystems        | Cannot link across filesystems               |
| Can link directories               | Usually cannot link directories              |
| Breaks if original file is deleted | Still works even if original file is deleted |

  

  | Command | Purpose                                                       | Example                    |
| ------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| `cut`   | Extract specific columns/fields from a file                   | `cut -d',' -f1 data.csv`   |
| `tee`   | Display output on screen and save it to a file simultaneously | `ls \| tee output.txt`     |
| `sort`  | Sort lines alphabetically or numerically                      | `sort names.txt`           |
| `clear` | Clear the terminal screen                                     | `clear`                    |
| `diff`  | Compare two files line by line                                | `diff file1.txt file2.txt` |


  
  | Action              | Command        |
